    "description": "The Doors are a gambling clicker for memorization and luck. Suitable for all ages. Click on the doors and collect the crystals before the time runs out. To see what is hiding behind the doors – roll the dice, they will open the randomly dropped number of doors. Remember what's behind them, and open others at your own risk.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBehind the doors can be: crystals, various enemies, or advantages in the form of additional dice rolls, time, health and treasure. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nNice graphics and sounds create a relaxing atmosphere. Complete all 20 levels! With each level, the number of doors increases, there are more enemies, there are closed doors to which you need to look for keys! At the same time, the game remains both challenging and relaxing at the same time! <br />\r\nFor every 10,000 points, a mini bonus game is given. Score as many points as possible so that everyone knows that you are the best in the game!!!",
